It is not possible to build graphics/gimp on any system, for several months.
Have built many systems. In ALL cases, gimp (2.8) fails to build because
graphics/libopenraw doesn't support devel/boost* since 1.52.0_2 - 9 months ago!
gimp, depending on libopenraw, has not been buildable since. Is Gimp abandoned?

